5927+00:00", "source_avatar_url": "", "source_id": "fb_twharmonica", "source_name": "Taiwan Harmonica Music Festival", "text": "🌟 本次2026臺灣口琴音樂節，將匯聚來自亞洲各國的口琴演奏家同台演奏！一個此次邀請的重量級團體是甫獲得世界口琴節小合奏冠軍以及大合奏組亞軍肯定，來自韓國的新生代團體首爾獨奏家口琴樂團 (Seoul Soloists Harmonica Orchestra) ! 💪\n首爾獨奏家口琴樂團（Seoul Soloists Harmonica Orchestra, SSHO）是以口琴獨奏家暨指揮朴鍾聲（Jongseong Park 박종성 Jong seong Park）為核心所創立的韓國口琴樂團。樂團由韓國優秀的口琴演奏家組成，成員包括主修口琴演奏的專業音樂家，以及多位曾於國際比賽中獲獎的演奏者。\n自 2018 年首場音樂會以來，SSHO 曾受邀於多個重要場館演出，包括首爾藝術殿堂 IBK 室內樂廳（IBK Chamber Hall at Seoul Arts Center）及 The House Concert 等。樂團也曾於 Naru Arts Center、Daegu BS Arts & Culture Center、White Wave Art Center 等場地舉辦專場音樂會。2024 年，SSHO 受邀於中國舉行的亞太口琴節擔任音樂會演出嘉賓，逐漸在國際舞台上受到更多矚目。2025 年，樂團參加於德國舉辦的世界口琴節，榮獲重奏組第一名及大合奏組第二名，並獲得觀眾與評審的高度讚賞。\nSSHO 致力於拓展口琴演奏的藝術可能性，重視細膩的音樂詮釋與精緻的表現力。同時，樂團也持續探索新的音樂想法，追求兼具精湛技巧與情感深度的演出。如今，SSHO 正逐步跨越韓國，成為國際舞台上備受矚目的口琴樂團之一。\n--\n🌟 The 2026 Taiwan Harmonica Music Festival will bring together harmonica artists from across Asia to perform on the same stage. An importent invited ensemble this year is the Seoul Soloists Harmonica Orchestra from Korea, a rising new-generation group that has recently been recognized as the first prize of the Ensemble Category and the 1st runner-up of the Orchestra Category at the World Harmonica Festival! 💪\nSeoul Soloists Harmonica Orchestra (SSHO) is a Korean harmonica orchestra founded around harmonica soloist and conductor Jongseong Park. The orchestra is made up of some of Korea’s finest harmonica players, including professional musicians who majored in harmonica performance as well as prize winners from various international competitions.\nSince its debut concert in 2018, SSHO has been invited to perform at prestigious venues such as the IBK Chamber Hall at Seoul Art", "url": "https://www.facebook.com/twharmonica/posts/pfbid02ivogqTGGrZFPqSGXYFE6hy74PStFMaRa9fq5H5MPfs9x9rUYd1mixTzosn6GxWxEl"}
