{"account": "https://youtube.com/SiriusHARP", "image_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HAU2LhpkLFU/maxresdefault.jpg", "images": ["https://i.ytimg.com/vi/HAU2LhpkLFU/maxresdefault.jpg"], "include_without_keywords": true, "key": "yt_siriusharp:HAU2LhpkLFU", "keyword_matches": ["口琴", "演出", "影片", "harmonica"], "llm_categories": ["posts-videos"], "llm_confidence": 1.0, "llm_labels": ["口琴", "演出", "影片", "公開更新"], "llm_model": "mimo-v2.5", "llm_reason": "貼文分享天狼星口琴樂團於德國口琴節與口琴家合作的演出影片，內容明確涉及口琴樂團與演奏者，屬口琴相關公開更新。", "llm_relevant": true, "llm_tagged_at": "2026-06-23T19:20:04.840960+00:00", "matched_keywords": ["口琴", "演出", "影片", "公開更新"], "media_type": "video", "platform": "youtube", "post_id": "HAU2LhpkLFU", "posted_at": "2025-04-10T10:38:04+00:00", "raw_source": "yt-dlp", "seen_at": "2026-06-23T15:11:41.855318+00:00", "source_avatar_url": "", "source_id": "yt_siriusharp", "source_name": "Sirius Harmonica Ensemble", "text": "Atemlos durch die Nacht - 天狼星口琴樂團 Sirius Harmonica Ensemble feat. Konstantin Reinfeld\n此影片為天狼星口琴樂團參與Harmonica FEN Festival 期間，於德國柏林Kesselhaus in der Kulturbrauerei邀請十孔口琴家Konstantin Reinfeld一起拍攝\n《Atemlos durch die Nacht》（意為「屏息穿越夜晚」）是德國女歌手海倫娜·費雪（Helene Fischer）於2013年發行的代表作，由克莉絲蒂娜·巴赫創作。這首流行舞曲節奏輕快，旋律朗朗上口，描繪戀人間沉醉於愛情與自由的夜晚情感。歌曲在德國、奧地利等德語國家大受歡迎，成為費雪最廣為人知的作品之一，也奠定了她在德國流行音樂界的地位。\nThis video was filmed during the Sirius Harmonica Ensemble’s participation in the Harmonica FEN Festival, at the Kesselhaus in der Kulturbrauerei in Berlin, Germany, together with Konstantin Reinfeld.\n“Atemlos durch die Nacht” (“Breathless Through the Night”) is a signature hit by German pop singer Helene Fischer, released in 2013 and written by Kristina Bach. With its catchy melody and upbeat rhythm, the song captures the feeling of being lost in love and freedom during a magical night. Hugely popular in German-speaking countries, it became one of Fischer’s most iconic songs and solidified her status as a major star in the German pop music scene.\n十孔口琴 Diatonic Harmonica | Konstantin Reinfeld\n