 However, it was only in August 2024, during the 10th Manouche de Piracicaba Jazz Festival, that they met in person for the first time. And in this short and exciting season together in Piracicaba, São Paulo and Curitiba, they performed several concerts and also, finally, recorded together in the same studio, with the Hot Club of Piracicaba.\nYen-Hua Wang has a solid work with harmonica. She is also a member of Sirius Harmonica Ensemble and Punch Harmonica Ensemb", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i_R0WpD4DrE"}
