{"account": "https://youtube.com/channel/UCyCPSbKpVa9oaAAqCRjcvZA", "image_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8afwZxFCl1M/maxresdefault.jpg", "images": ["https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8afwZxFCl1M/maxresdefault.jpg"], "include_without_keywords": true, "key": "yt_ucycpsbkpva9oaaaqcrjcvza:8afwZxFCl1M", "keyword_matches": [], "llm_categories": ["posts-videos"], "llm_confidence": 0.85, "llm_labels": ["口琴", "影片", "公開更新"], "llm_model": "mimo-v2.5", "llm_reason": "來源為口琴五重奏「111 Quintet」，內容是其錄製的口琴演奏影片，符合口琴演奏者公開更新。", "llm_relevant": true, "llm_tagged_at": "2026-06-23T19:27:26.569539+00:00", "matched_keywords": ["口琴", "影片", "公開更新"], "media_type": "video", "platform": "youtube", "post_id": "8afwZxFCl1M", "posted_at": "2026-02-13T01:04:00+00:00", "raw_source": "yt-dlp", "seen_at": "2026-06-23T15:21:47.402845+00:00", "source_avatar_url": "", "source_id": "yt_ucycpsbkpva9oaaaqcrjcvza", "source_name": "111 Quintet", "text": "Primavera Porteña\n｜布宜諾斯艾利斯之春 選段\n｜Astor Piazzolla（arr. Yora Chen 陳瑤容）\n寒意未散，脈動已起。\n｜Primavera Porteña｜布宜諾斯艾利斯之春 選段｜皮耶左拉（編曲：陳瑤容）\n在皮耶左拉筆下，「春」不是溫柔的風景而是在張力之中重新奪回的動能。\n聲部彼此牽引、交織與推進，城市在冷冽空氣中逐步甦醒。\n農曆新春之際，願我們\n在變動之中保有平安，在冷冽之中生出勇氣，在時間之中持續生長。\n迎向新的開始。\n2026.01.29 於亞門音像錄製\nWinter has not yet withdrawn,but the pulse begins to move.\n｜Primavera Porteña (Spring in Buenos Aires) – Excerpt\n｜Astor Piazzolla (arr. Yora Chen)\nIn Piazzolla’s language,spring is not a gentle landscape,but energy reclaimedthrough tension and resistance.\nVoices intertwine and propel one another,as a city slowly awakens in the cold air.\nAs we enter the Lunar New Year,may we find\npeace within change,courage within the cold,and growth through time.\nToward a new beginning.\n.\n2026.01.29 Recorded at AM Studio", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8afwZxFCl1M"}
